  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe [`lift_locks`](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/tree/lift-locks) branch contains some work to remove some `RwLock`-based race conditions from the `BeaconChain` \"seen caches\".\r\n\r\nThe following diff is my solution to this issue:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/compare/4b128ee8494b1775dd285c8d0f56b1a5025f1d20..dc76a3340c6b012ea0083343104889ae9831b8ce\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nTake the `lift_locks` branch, rebase it on master (or whatever git strategy you want) and get it ready to merge into master. Also, check that my changes are sane.\r\n",
